Katie Holmes, 43, showed off her natural beauty on a date with her new boyfriend, Bobby Wooten III, 33. The Dawson’s Creek actress was seen walking through the streets of New York clutching some takeaway food. She wore some baggy grey oversized trousers and a cosy fairisle knit jumper. The star moved her face mask to be under her chin, revealing her smile underneath. She and Bobby, who is a musician and composer, were first spotted in public together in April 2022. He has performed with stars including Jennifer Lopez, Mac Miller and Jennifer Hudson, and is currently touring with Carly Rae Jepson. Katie recently showed her support as he posted an Instagram video of a performance. She commented: “AMAZING!!!!!!” as she applauded her beau.